Installation Instructions
*************************

Copyright (C) 2010, Dmitrijs Ledkovs.

This file is free documentation; the copyright holders give unlimited permission
to copy, distribute and modify it.

Briefly, the shell command `./waf configure build install' should configure,
build, and install this package.

To see all available configuration options see `./waf configure --help'

Usuall environment variables are supported, e.g. CFLAGS.
